00:04:11.530 --> 00:04:13.610
You should know this organization.

00:04:13.610 --> 00:04:18.990
They publish America's greatest
writers in affordable, attractive,

00:04:18.990 --> 00:04:23.940
authoritative, uniformly
bound books.

00:04:23.940 --> 00:04:27.130
If you pick the greatest
authors in America

00:04:27.130 --> 00:04:31.400
and what they do will actually
8 to 10 volumes a year.

00:04:31.400 --> 00:04:35.310 position:56%
I would just add as a plug for them,
they make wonderful wedding gifts,

00:04:35.310 --> 00:04:39.000
birthday gifts, anniversary
